# unprompted-flow-qa — consumption model

- This package is **not** assumed to be on the public **npm** registry. Role Scout and other hosts typically use a **`file:`** dependency pointing at this repo (e.g. `"unprompted-flow-qa": "file:../../flow-qa"`).
- After changing this package, consumers must **`npm run build`** here, then **`npm install`** in the host app so the linked copy updates.
- Do not instruct users to `npm install unprompted-flow-qa@latest` unless they have **explicitly published** this package and switched the host to the registry version.
